  "title": "DELIVERY DRIVER CUM PLANNER",
  "description": "<p>Job Descriptions</p><ul><li>Operate and drive a 14’ truck safely and responsibly.</li><li>Ensure goods loaded onto the truck tally accurately with delivery orders.</li><li>Coordinate with team members to deliver goods to customers efficiently.</li><li>Plan and organize delivery schedules to optimize routes and timelines.</li><li>Perform any other duties as assigned by management.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 driving licence with a clean driving record.</li><li>Physically fit and able to handle delivery tasks.</li><li>Strong teamwork skills and a positive working attitude.</li><li>Willingness to work overtime when required.</li><li>Punctual, reliable, and responsible.</li></ul><p>Working Hours</p><ul><li>Monday to Friday: 9:00 am – 6:00 pm</li><li>Saturday: 9:00 am – 1:00 pm</li></ul><p>Remuneration: Basic salary + OT + Incentives up to $4,200 to $5,200.  Increment after 3 months probation. Year-end bonus, etc.</p><p>Benefits: Annual leave, Sick leave,Childcare leave, etc.</p><h3>Any candidateinterest send resume via WhatApp 98330586 or email finz.mgr@gmail.com</h3>",
